Title: Who known tomorrow
DateModified: '2019-02-01'
DatePublished: '2019-02-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/who-known-tomorrow
SetInCountry: Argentina
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Seth Blee Tetteh
AuthorCountry: Ghana
Text: In some years a setting tooth became a great footballer in the world even his
  people never dream about it.Because of hard work and grace God that footballer proved
  his great talant that God gave to him.This great footballer was a man people didn't
  respect him and believe as he can play as his playin.They said humble yourself and
  God will raised you up and is true the man humble and true his humble God raised
  him up.This story is about Lionel Messi Argentina international and Christian Ronaldo
  Portuguese international and I want my testimony be like them.In all my liaI always
  played that all my dreams may comes as Lionel Messi and Christian Rinaldo dream
  comes.Am on it making practice on it and praying of it.One thing that am asking
  from God that he should make a way for me to get that opportunity and also pray
  that I may not lost when I get the opportunity.I want to be a good footballer like
  Rinaldo and Lionel Messi and some of the good footballers in European football.I
  want  my story to be told all over the world and people see how great is the Almighty
  God he is when a get the opportunity to play in the European football.I will be
  happy of this when the opportunity comes and work hard as I dream and pray of it.I
  will not be lazzy but work hard. May God be my favour and my dream and story comes
  true
